2019s feedback.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_separator color=&#8221;custom&#8221; el_width=&#8221;30&#8243; accent_color=&#8221;#e0e0e0&#8243;][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/5&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;11927&#8243; alignment=&#8221;right&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;4\/5&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1705939411499{padding-right: 70px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h6 style=\"color: #026da4;\"><strong><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Engaged, Community-Oriented Remote Team<\/span><\/strong><\/h6>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">We are a fully distributed team, but maintain a strong sense of collegiality and community, and are genuinely interested in learning more about each other. We create and enjoy intentional opportunities to connect, and celebrate each other\u2019s highlights\u2014 big or small, at work, and outside work.<\/span>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/5&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;11928&#8243; alignment=&#8221;right&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;4\/5&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h6><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Flexibility<\/span><\/h6>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">We value flexibility to support our team holistically, and prioritize results over rigid schedules.<\/span>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/5&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;11990&#8243; alignment=&#8221;right&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;4\/5&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1705939429175{padding-right: 70px !i