ext-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">unlimited additional flexible<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\"> paid time off. The company closes for <\/span><strong><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">13 paid<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\"> holidays, observes <\/span><strong><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">half day Fridays<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\"> year-round, and closes between Christmas and New Years.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=&#8221;11931&#8243; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Health and Wellness<\/span><\/h6>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Our benefits package includes employer-sponsored, <strong>comprehensive medical, dental, and vision insurance<\/strong>, as well as life and disability insurance. We encourage our team to make time for rest and to do things that fill their wellness bucket by offering a wellness reimbursement.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=&#8221;11930&#8243; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Financial Perks<\/span><\/h6>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Our benefits include an <\/span><strong><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">employer-matched 403(b) retirement plan<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"OYPEnA text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">,<\/span>